msgid ""
"\n"
"            If your customer runs on Odoo 18 or higher, customer data and "
"sales order lines\n"
"            will be automatically created. Any other pdf containing an "
"attached\n"
"            UBL-RequestForQuotation file will work as well.\n"
"        "
